schools.name: Amy Biehl Community School At Rancho Viejo

data.description: Excellent buy in a hot market. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a 1 car garage in the highly sought after Rancho Viejo. This home is in excellent condition and is ready for a new owner. Sighted on a quiet street and is convenient with easy access to 599, I-25, or anywhere in Santa Fe. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer will convey to the new owner. Refrigerated air for these hot days. This home will sell quickly so schedule to see right away!
